WHAT THIS REPOSITORY IS
    A domain-specific IDENTITY package: the wiring, routing (the closed
    track), predeliberated decision tuples, playbooks, ratified
    configuration doctrine, documentation, and (where present) reference
    spoke implementations that give an AI agent swarm a governed operating
    identity for a specific field. This is the value-bearing work. It is
    NOT the open chassis it runs on (dispatcher-agents, Apache-2.0) and is
    NOT licensed under the chassis's terms.

